# Education Performance & Resource Allocation Dashboard

## Project Overview
Dashboard for analyzing student performance, attendance, pass vs fail ratio, and resource allocation using Power BI visualizations.

## Files Included
- Education Dashboard.jpeg
- education_dataset.xlsx

## Tools Used
- Excel / Power BI
- GitHub

## Features
- Average Marks Analysis
- Attendance Analysis
- Pass vs Fail Distribution
- Resource Usage Analysis
- Interactive Dashboard













